Package simulator

Contains the necessary methods to implement the discrete stochastic simulation
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DicreteEvent
    Discrete Event interface.
    PendingEventContainer
    Interface of a Pending Event Container Store a set of events sorted by some sort of parameter (for example: time, etc..)
    Traverser
    Interface of a graph traverser.
    TraverserPath
    Interface of a graph path.

    Public Class: Comparador.Java This class implements the interface comparator from java.util The comparator is used to compare two objects that implements the Interface DiscreteEvent.
